<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>ὑπόμνημα Ζήνωνι 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Παθιώφιος. ἐνεύχο-

    <lb n="3"/>μαί σοι τὴν Ἀπολλωνίου 

    <lb n="4"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σω</unclear>τηρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ία</unclear>ν, καθά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>ερ μοι 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐπηγγείλω, <choice><corr>ἀφεῖναι</corr><sic>αφε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ις</unclear></sic></choice> τὴν 

    <lb n="6"/>γυναῖκά μου, ὅπως μὴ 

    <lb n="7"/>συμβῆι αὐτῆι παραπολέσθαι 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐν τῶ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>εσμωτηρίωι 

    <lb n="9"/>ἀθύμως διακειμένηι 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐπὶ τοῖς παιδίοις ἐγώ τε 

    <lb n="11"/>δύνωμαι πρὸς τῆι ἐργασίαι 

    <lb n="12"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γίνεσθ</unclear>αι. εἰς δὲ τὸ λοιπόν, 

    <lb n="13"/>ἐά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> ἡμᾶς λάβηις τοιοῦτό τι 

    <lb n="14"/>διαπραττομένους, οὐ παραιτού-

    <lb n="15"/>μεθα, ἀλλὰ χρῆσαι ἡμῖν ὡς 

    <lb n="16"/>βούλει. ὥσπερ οὖν διατελεῖς 

    <lb n="17"/>πάντας <choice><corr>σῴζων</corr><sic>σωιζων</sic></choice> καὶ οὐθεὶς 

    <lb n="18"/>διὰ σοῦ οὐθὲν πέποσχεν ἄτο-

    <lb n="19"/>πον, καὶ ἐμὲ δεόμενόν σου 

    <lb n="20"/>ἐλέησον. 

    <lb n="21"/>εὐτύχει. </ab></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-226" notBefore="-275" type="textDate">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Datierung nach dem Rahmen des Zenon - Archivs.</p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59482</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1120</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59482</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;3;59482" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Philadelphia</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.1120" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=3&amp;vNum=59482"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>